# Commands Quick Reference

```bash
# Install dependencies
flutter pub get

# Generate localization code (after ARB edits)
flutter gen-l10n

# Generate Hive adapters (after Hive model edits)
dart run build_runner build --delete-conflicting-outputs

# Format changed files
dart format lib/ test/

# Static analysis (with fatal infos, as CI does)
dart analyze --fatal-infos lib test

# Run all tests
flutter test

# Run a single test file
flutter test test/path/to/specific_test.dart

# Run a single test by name
flutter test --name "test name pattern" test/path/to/file.dart

# Platform builds (release)
flutter build apk --release --split-per-abi
flutter build ios --release --no-codesign
flutter build macos --release
flutter build windows --release
flutter build linux --release

# Check untranslated messages (CI script)
python3 .github/scripts/check_no_new_untranslated.py <base_desiredFileName.txt> desiredFileName.txt
```

# CI Workflows

`.github/workflows/` 中的工作流：

- `pr-check.yml` — PR：`dart format`（变更文件）、`flutter gen-l10n` + diff 检查、未翻译检查、`dart analyze --fatal-infos`、`flutter test`
- `build-stable.yml` — 手动多平台 release 构建（含 secrets 注入）
- `build-stable-38.yml`、`build-stable-41.yml` — 旧 Flutter 版本构建变体
- `build-linux-arm64.yml` — Linux ARM64
- `build.yml`、`bulid-stable-38-new.yml` — 其他构建变体

**触碰 build、版本号或 secrets 注入时，必须检查所有相似 workflow 文件并保持同步。**
